domains.name: ELISpot Assay Test Batch Fields
domains.description: Define the batch properties for this assay design. The user is prompted for these properties once for each set of runs they import to this assay.

domains.name: ELISpot Assay Test Run Fields
domains.description: Define the run properties for this assay design. The user is prompted for these properties once per run and they will be applied to all rows in the run.

domains.name: ELISpot Assay Test Sample Fields
domains.description: Define the sample properties for this assay design. The user will be prompted to enter these properties for each of the sample well groups in their chosen plate template.

domains.name: ELISpot Assay Test Antigen Fields
domains.description: Define the antigen properties for this assay design. The user will be prompted to enter these properties for each of the antigen well groups in their chosen plate template.

domains.name: ELISpot Assay Test Analyte Fields
domains.description: Define the analyte properties for this assay design. The user will be prompted to enter these properties for each of the analyte well groups

data.name: ELISpot Assay Test
data.description: This is the description for the ELISpot assay design.
